{"title":"翻转游戏","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2946","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>现有n个数字a<sub>1</sub>,a<sub>2</sub>...a<sub>n</sub>，其值均为0或1。</p>\n<p>要求对着n个数中连续的若干个数进行一次取反（0-&gt;1,1-&gt;0)，求所能得到的最多的1的数目。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行，n</p>\n<p>第二行，n个数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>能得到的最多的1的数目</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<pre>4<br>1 0 0 1</pre>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<pre>4</pre>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>1 ≤ </span><em>n</em><span> ≤ 100</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}